sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Admin/GitOps
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as rhods-operator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)
    participant Controller as rhods-operator Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Renderer as Manifest Renderer<br/>Kustomize Engine
    participant Manifests as /opt/manifests<br/>220+ Manifest Sets
    participant Components as Component Namespaces<br/>redhat-ods-applications
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation and Component Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply DataScienceCluster CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>kubectl credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate CR<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>Webhook: Validate spec fields<br/>Set default values
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: CR event (watch)<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>Controller: Reconcile DataScienceCluster
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Component CRs<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>Renderer: Render component manifests<br/>in-process
    Renderer->>Manifests: Read Kustomize manifests<br/>filesystem
    Manifests-->>Renderer: Manifest YAML
    Renderer->>Renderer: Apply Kustomize overlays<br/>(odh/rhoai variants)
    Renderer-->>Controller: Rendered manifests

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Deploy manifests to namespaces<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Components: Create Deployments, Services,<br/>ConfigMaps, Secrets
    Components-->>K8sAPI: Resource created
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Success

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update DSC status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Monitoring and Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: Authorized
    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>via kube-rbac-proxy
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(controller_runtime_*, component_*)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Webhook Validation (CR Update)

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl edit DataScienceCluster<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>kubectl credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate update<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>Webhook: Validate component changes<br/>Check dependency requirements

    alt Validation Success
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR updated
    else Validation Failure
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Denied (error message)
        K8sAPI-->>User: Validation error
    end

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: DSCInitialization (Platform Services)

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply DSCInitialization CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate CR<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
    K8sAPI->>Controller: CR event (watch)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Auth CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Monitoring CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMesh CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Deploy ServiceMonitors,<br/>PrometheusRules<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Deploy Prometheus, Alertmanager,<br/>Tempo StatefulSets<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Platform services deployed
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update DSCI status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
